                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22Adoption%20of%20Deep-Learning%20Models%20for%20Managing%20Threat%20in%20API%20Calls%20with%20Transparency%20Obligation%20Practice%20for%20Overall%20Resilience&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/2887108%3A%0A%0AAdoption%20of%20Deep-Learning%20Models%20for%20Managing%20Threat%20in%20API%20Calls%20with%20Transparency%20Obligation%20Practice%20for%20Overall%20Resilience%0A%0AAbstract%3A%20System-to-system%20communication%20via%20Application%20Programming%20Interfaces%20%28APIs%29%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20seamless%20interaction%20among%20software%20applications%20and%20systems%20for%20efficient%20and%20automated%20service%20delivery.%20APIs%20facilitate%20the%20exchange%20of%20data%20and%20functionalities%20across%20diverse%20platforms%2C%20enhancing%20operational%20efficiency%20and%20user%20experience.%20However%2C%20this%20also%20introduces%20potential%20vulnerabilities%20that%20attackers%20can%20exploit%20to%20compromise%20system%20security%2C%20highlighting%20the%20importance%20of%20identifying%20and%20mitigating%20associated%20security%20risks.%20By%20examining%20the%20weaknesses%20inherent%20in%20these%20APIs%20using%20security%20open-intelligence%20catalogues%20like%20CWE%20and%20CAPEC%20and%20implementing%20controls%20from%20NIST%20SP%20800-53%2C%20organizations%20can%20significantly%20enhance%20their%20security%20posture%2C%20safeguarding%20their%20data%20and%20systems%20against%20potential%20threats.%20However%2C%20this%20task%20is%20challenging%20due%20to%20evolving%20threats%20and%20vulnerabilities.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20is%20challenging%20to%20analyse%20threats%20given%20the%20large%20volume%20of%20traffic%20generated%20from%20API%20calls.%20This%20work%20contributes%20to%20tackling%20this%20challenge%20and%20makes%20a%20novel%20contribution%20to%20managing%20threats%20within%20system-to-system%20communication%20through%20API%20calls.%20It%20introduces[...]" title="Ema